default&#xa0;
default1.6
default              
defaultThe short time between the barriers descending and the train arriving on AHBC is certainly in contrast to the long waits that are often experienced at full barrier crossings, which are usually oper
defaultated from a 
defaultꞋ
defaultlocal
defaultꞋ 
defaultsignal box (local does not mean that all such crossings are readily viewed from the signal box - many are viewed 
